      <header>

        <h2 class="node__title">
          <a href="/en/story/2024/05/1149321" rel="bookmark"><span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden">UN agencies warn of imminent starvation risk in Sudan’s Darfur region</span>
</a>
        </h2>

        <div class="node__meta">
          
                      
            <div class="field field--name-field-news-date field--type-datetime field--label-hidden field__item"><time datetime="2024-05-03T12:00:00Z" class="datetime">3 May 2024</time>
</div>
      
                          
            <div class="field field--name-field-news-topics field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item"><a href="/en/news/topic/peace-and-security" hreflang="en">Peace and Security</a></div>
      
                        
                    <p class="minimal-share"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://news.un.org/en/story/2024/05/1149321" title="Share this via Facebook" class="facebook" data-ms="facebook">Facebook</a>
<a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=UN agencies warn of imminent starvation risk in Sudan’s Darfur region&amp;url=https://news.un.org/en/story/2024/05/1149321" title="Share this via Twitter" class="twitter" data-ms="twitter">Twitter</a>
</p>

        </div>

      </header>
      <div class="node__content clearfix">

        
        
            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-news-story-lead field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>UN agencies issued a joint warning on Friday that time is running out to prevent starvation in Sudan’s Darfur region due to intensifying clashes around the northern capital of El Fasher, which are hindering efforts to deliver lifesaving aid.</p>
</div>
      
        

      </div>
