        <h2 class="node__title">
          <a href="/en/story/2024/04/1148791" rel="bookmark"><span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden">War in Sudan is ‘a crisis of epic proportions’ as atrocities abound</span>
</a>
        </h2>

        <div class="node__meta">
          
                      
            <div class="field field--name-field-news-date field--type-datetime field--label-hidden field__item"><time datetime="2024-04-19T12:00:00Z" class="datetime">19 April 2024</time>
</div>
      
                          
            <div class="field field--name-field-news-topics field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item"><a href="/en/news/topic/peace-and-security" hreflang="en">Peace and Security</a></div>
      
                        
                    <p class="minimal-share"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://news.un.org/en/story/2024/04/1148791" title="Share this via Facebook" class="facebook" data-ms="facebook">Facebook</a>
<a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=War in Sudan is ‘a crisis of epic proportions’ as atrocities abound&amp;url=https://news.un.org/en/story/2024/04/1148791" title="Share this via Twitter" class="twitter" data-ms="twitter">Twitter</a>
</p>

        </div>

      </header>
      <div class="node__content clearfix">

        
        
            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-news-story-lead field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p><span lang="EN-GB">The year-long ongoing war in Sudan is “a crisis of epic proportions”, and the world must rethink the way it supports the Sudanese people amid rampant atrocities against civilians and no end in sight, top UN and African Union officials warned the Security Council on Friday.</span></p>
</div>
      
        

